{"tid":2442551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5歲女童疑遭親父繼母虐殺 身有133處新舊傷口","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T00:19:39.000Z","uid":126919,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"839bc6ca84ae1937ab7640e00c92a1182b973f1a","tid":2442551,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"法醫今供稱，女童的頭部、四肢及身軀共有133處新舊傷口，頭皮深層瘀傷致皮下出血，相信她曾遭重複掌摑、拳打或硬物施襲，並在死前兩天內被拋上天花板撞到頭部達10次或以上。此外，女童身上有多處細菌感染引致的潰瘍，引致多個器官受感染，最終死於敗血病。法醫又透露，胸腺作為兒童的重要免疫系統器官，10歲或以下健康兒童的胸腺重量至少16克，但Z的胸腺僅重5克。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/KSRHZYHNQVGHHGWHRDGWJA5SAA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FKSRHZYHNQVGHHGWHRDGWJA5SAA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHYgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=e79d2a62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FKSRHZYHNQVGHHGWHRDGWJA5SAA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=9b0264db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/KSRHZYHNQVGHHGWHRDGWJA5SAA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"6566bf4a79d10cc6d8db0bd34f0ffddc3e858058","tid":2442551,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"頭部方面，Z的眼角、鼻樑及嘴唇，均佈滿新近造成的瘀傷或擦傷。其顱骨佈滿瘀傷，部份是死前兩天內造成，腦部細胞亦受損。她相信，Z要被人拋上天花板並撞到頭部達10次或以上，才有可能造成該傷勢。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839e257efb0460e29dcd1ebde76f671443719c39","tid":2442551,"uid":239321,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"其實果兩公婆係咪弱智人士？<br />\n做乜鳩拋個細路上天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c14053dda420d61c42772594eeb2440eedecb8","tid":2442551,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:17:03.000Z","msg":"Z身上有多處大小各異、細菌感染引致的潰瘍，當中背部及右膝各有兩處大面積的深層潰瘍，相信至少在死前三周造成。<br />\n<br />\n死前三週&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"3b21aacfe713af8b1488fc295e055f2d5df1010b","tid":2442551,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:19:11.000Z","msg":"哥哥當時傷勢<br />\n<br />\n為男童X驗傷的法醫傅家聰則供稱，X的軀幹及四肢佈滿疤痕、結痂中的傷口及新舊瘀傷，其臀部則有潰瘍。傅指，推測有關傷勢是長時間被硬物襲擊造成，而根據傷勢位置及X的年齡，相信是受虐造成。<br />\n<br />\n傅又指，瘀傷一般不會留下疤痕，相信X被籐條或地拖襲擊後形成撕裂性傷口，卻沒經過恰當護理致情況惡化，最終傷口癒合並留下疤痕。至於其臀部的潰瘍，他強調使用酒精消毒並不會促進傷口癒合，必須接受專業護理。<br />\n<br />\n傳表示，就X的整體傷勢而言，他絕對需要接受專業醫學護理，否則絕對會影響其日常生活，例如臀部潰瘍會令他難以坐下，雙腳傷勢亦會影響走動。"},{"pid":"b7314390e2097d85cf62a0a16d9471669f6c2a0e","tid":2442551,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"839e257efb0460e29dcd1ebde76f671443719c39","tid":2442551,"uid":239321,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"其實果兩公婆係咪弱智人士？<br />\n做乜鳩拋個細路上天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得要用個撞字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ef0ceb161b2ca9f8459daf4158c4a737